  "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
  "body": "## Bug Report\r\n\r\nDeployment: 1 tikv + 1 rngine\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20279863/75034777-ea673680-54e8-11ea-84ea-2a4b4c95f403.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20279863/75034772-e6d3af80-54e8-11ea-86fd-61d8d786f3aa.png)\r\n\r\nThere is only one region in TiKV. After the TiKV instance is restarted, the peer in this TiKV campaigns to become a leader. Then it hibernated immediately and do not send any message to the learner. After 5min, the leader wakes up and finally send a heartbeat to learner.\r\n",
